Privacy Policy for Brawl Legend

Brawl Legend values your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how the Bot collects, uses, and safeguards your information.

1. Information We Collect

The Bot only collects information provided by users through direct interactions. This includes, but is not limited to:

Commands issued by users to the Bot.

Data entered by users, such as messages, IDs, or any other content provided in response to the Botâ€™s prompts.

2. How We Use Your Information

The data collected is used exclusively to provide the intended functionality of the Bot. Examples include:

Processing commands and generating responses.

Storing user preferences or settings to enhance user experience.

3. Data Storage and Retention

The Bot stores data only as long as it is necessary for functionality or as required by the specific features used.

Once the data is no longer needed, it is securely deleted from our systems.

4. Data Sharing

We do not share, sell, or disclose user data to third parties except as required by law or to comply with legal obligations.

5. Security Measures

We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no system can guarantee 100% security.

6. User Control and Rights

The Bot does not collect information unless explicitly provided by the user through interactions.

7. Updates to the Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be announced in the global help server.
